307
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:37,990
I and your military will carry out your solemn biddings.

308
00:27:37,990 --> 00:27:40,810
Your grace is immeasurable, Your Majesty!

309
00:27:40,810 --> 00:27:45,590
Your grace is immeasurable, Your Majesty!

